{"Id":486,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-mazhonggang","Author":"Ma Zhong Gang","Language":"Chinese(simplified)","Description":"Chinese(simplified)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"https://alquran.cloud/api","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"艾布•拉赫布[注] [意即火焰之父，是穆圣的一位叔父]的双手将要被毁灭，他也将被毁灭。"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他的财富和他所获得的[如儿女]将对他毫无益处。"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他将进入有焰的烈火[中烧灼]，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"他的搬柴的妻子[她常在穆圣经过的路上布设尖刺，到处诽谤穆圣]也将进入[有焰的烈火中烧灼]，"},{"SurahNumber":111,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"她的脖子上拴着一根结实的棕榈绳。"}]}